OL,3,CThe story behind legendary Clough/
OL,4,CRevie interview 50 years on
OL,6,FFifty years ago an interview took
OL,7,Fplace in the studios at the then
OL,8,FYorkshire Television centre that would
OL,9,Fgo down in both football and
OL,10,Ftelevision history.
OL,12,FBilled "Goodbye Mr Clough", the
OL,13,Fspecial Calendar programme brought
OL,14,Ftogether two former Leeds United
OL,15,Fmanagers, the newly sacked Brian
OL,16,FClough and long-serving Don Revie, for
OL,17,Fa must-watch 25-minute conversation.
