OL,3,CThe story behind legendary Clough/
OL,4,CRevie interview 50 years on
OL,6,FThe interview was a fiery affair, with
OL,7,Fpresenter Austin Mitchell stoking the
OL,8,Fflames and allowing the two men to
OL,9,Frile each other.
OL,11,FThroughout the programme - broadcast
OL,12,Fon 12 September 1974 - Clough and
OL,13,FRevie locked horns in what was already
OL,14,Fa frosty relationship, after Clough
OL,15,Fsaid that Revie's Leeds United should
OL,16,Fhave been relegated over their
OL,17,Fdisciplinary record.
