OL,3,CThe story behind legendary Clough/
OL,4,CRevie interview 50 years on
OL,6,FThe interview went on to inspire
OL,7,Fauthor David Peace to write the book
OL,8,FThe Dammed United - the story of
OL,9,FClough's short-lived tenure at Leeds.
OL,10,FIt would later be made into a film
OL,11,Fstarring Micheal Sheen and a stage
OL,12,Fplay.
OL,14,FWhat happened before the interview?
OL,16,FBrian Clough had been at Leeds United
OL,17,Ffor all of 44 days when he was sacked
OL,18,Fas the club's manager.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G3/13
