OL,3,CThe story behind legendary Clough/
OL,4,CRevie interview 50 years on
OL,6,FHe had taken over from Don Revie, who
OL,7,Fgained hero status during 13 years at
OL,8,FElland Road before going on to become
OL,9,FEngland's manager.
OL,11,FIn Revie's time as manager between
OL,12,F1961 and 1974 the club were a dominant
OL,13,Fforce in English football, winning the
OL,14,Fleague twice and the FA Cup in 1972.
OL,16,FPrior to joining the club, Clough had
OL,17,Fbeen outspoken in his criticism of
OL,18,FRevie's Leeds.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G4/13
