OL,3,CThe story behind legendary Clough/
OL,4,CRevie interview 50 years on
OL,6,FLifelong Leeds United fan Heidi Hague
OL,7,Fsays fans were surprised over the
OL,8,Fdecision to bring on Clough. She said:
OL,9,F"The general feeling around all the
OL,10,Ffans was no one wanted him to be
OL,11,Fthere."
OL,13,FShe added: "We thought we'd never be
OL,14,Fable to follow Leeds again because it
OL,15,Fwas just so bad."
OL,17,FThe animosity between the players and
OL,18,Fthe manager bled onto the pitch, with
OL,19,FClough winning just one of his first
OL,20,Fsix matches.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G5/13
