OL,3,CThe story behind legendary Clough/
OL,4,CRevie interview 50 years on
OL,6,FAfter being sacked after just seven
OL,7,Fweeks, Clough said: "I think it's a
OL,8,Fvery sad day for Leeds and a very sad
OL,9,Fday for football. Everything involved
OL,10,Fwith Leeds is just a little bit sad at
OL,11,Fthe moment."
OL,13,FThe interview
OL,15,FNow widely regarded as one of the most
OL,16,Ffamous sporting interviews of all
OL,17,Ftime, the team behind the broadcast
OL,18,Fsay they had no idea it would go on to
OL,19,Fbe so "monumental".
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G6/13
