OL,3,CThe story behind legendary Clough/
OL,4,CRevie interview 50 years on
OL,6,FGraham Ironside, Calendar's news
OL,7,Feditor at the time, was responsible
OL,8,Ffor getting the two men into the
OL,9,Fstudio which, given their mutual
OL,10,Fdislike for one another, wasn't an
OL,11,Feasy feat.
OL,13,FHe said: "We didn't think they'd be
OL,14,Fhappy with the prospect but we
OL,15,Fthought, we've got to try."
OL,17,FIt's believed the pair received
OL,18,Ffinancial incentives for the interview
OL,19,Famounting to around #400 each, along
OL,20,Fwith a pack of cigarettes for Clough.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G7/13
