OL,3,CThe story behind legendary Clough/
OL,4,CRevie interview 50 years on
OL,6,FA deliberate decision was made to sit
OL,7,Fthe pair in close proximity to one
OL,8,Fanother to heighten the intimacy, and
OL,9,Fthe inevitable friction.
OL,11,FIronside said: "It wasn't a football
OL,12,Finterview when you think about it, it
OL,13,Fwas between two stags at bay."
OL,15,FThe interview was conducted by
OL,16,Fpresenter Austin Mitchell, who acted
OL,17,Fas much as referee as interviewer.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G8/13
