OL,3,CThe story behind legendary Clough/
OL,4,CRevie interview 50 years on
OL,6,FThe director of Calendar at the time,
OL,7,FNick Gray, says the pair wanted to
OL,8,Fspeak to each other. He said: "It was
OL,9,Factually quite a cathartic thing for
OL,10,Fthem to actually come together and
OL,11,Fhave it out on television."
OL,13,FHe added: "We couldn't believe what
OL,14,Fwas happening, so we had to just
OL,15,Fcapture every moment of it in the best
OL,16,Fpossible way."
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G9/13
