OL,3,CThe story behind legendary Clough/
OL,4,CRevie interview 50 years on
OL,6,FA stand-out moment from the interview
OL,7,Fcame when Clough told Revie: "I want
OL,8,Fto win the league but I want to win it
OL,9,Fbetter," a comment which clearly irked
OL,10,Fthe legendary manager.
OL,12,FWhen asked who came out as the
OL,13,F"winner" of the interview, Ironside
OL,14,Fsaid: "There was no winner.
OL,16,F"What I thought afterwards is Clough
OL,17,Fwas a man in shock and Revie was a man
OL,18,Fdeeply hurt."
OL,20,FWhat happened after the interview?
