OL,3,CThe story behind legendary Clough/
OL,4,CRevie interview 50 years on
OL,6,FThe interview quickly became part of
OL,7,Ffootball folklore, and a major part of
OL,8,Fthe club's legacy.
OL,10,FThe day after the interview the
OL,11,Fnational publication, The Daily
OL,12,FExpress, printed the entire interview
OL,13,Fverbatim.
OL,15,FThirty years later, the story of Brian
OL,16,FClough's 44 days would be retold by
OL,17,FWest Yorkshire writer David Peace in
OL,18,Fthe book The Damed United.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1        G11/13
