OL,3,CThe story behind legendary Clough/
OL,4,CRevie interview 50 years on
OL,6,FPeace regards the Calendar interview
OL,7,Fas a major inspiration behind the book
OL,8,Fand remembers transcribing it at the
OL,9,Ftime at his home in Huddersfield.
OL,11,FHe said: "It was an excellent thing
OL,12,Ffor Calendar to have done. It was like
OL,13,Fa reprised fight that everyone in
OL,14,FYorkshire wanted to see."
OL,16,FIn 2009, a film version of the story
OL,17,Fwas released starring Michael Sheen as
OL,18,FBrian Clough and Colm Meany as Don
OL,19,FRevie.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1        G12/13
