OL,6,FA full version of the interview has
OL,7,Fbeen watched almost two million times
OL,8,Fon Youtube.
OL,10,FDiscussing the significance of the
OL,11,Finterview, Nick Gray said: "I don't
OL,12,Fthink a programme like the Clough and
OL,13,FRevie interview will happen like that
OL,14,Fagain, live on television."
